minnis , glenn " lenny bruce pardoned " , cbs news/associated press , december 23 , 2003    legacy bruce was the subject of the 1974 biographical film lenny directed by bob fosse and starring dustin hoffman ( in an academy award - nominated best actor role ) , and based on the broadway stage play of the same name written by julian barry and starring cliff gorman in his 1972 tony award winning role .

